      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MELANIA BANNER (2) produced a respectable 17.61 when filling a minor placing over 324m at Richmond Straight last start. Has the ability and expected to go close again. HEAR ME ROAR (8) boasts a strong record this journey with 10 wins and 13 minors from 30 tries. Missed the frame latest (17.63) when fourth over 324m at Richmond Straight in a NG. Looks one of the chances. HURRICANE ETHICS (4) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Airflow Betty (19.61) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to be in this for a long way. ROSCOE CONKLIN (7) is in the mix following a brief let-up.",
